  "title": "🚀 Customer Management Trainee (Entrepreneurial Track) – Entry Level",
  "description": "<p>Looking to build a strong foundation in <strong>business, communication & leadership</strong>? Join us as a Customer Management Trainee and gain hands-on exposure while progressing toward leadership roles with structured mentorship.</p><p>🌟 <strong>What You’ll Learn</strong></p><ul><li><p>Customer & account management</p></li><li><p>Communication & negotiation skills</p></li><li><p>Leadership & coaching fundamentals</p></li><li><p>Personal development & growth mindset</p></li></ul><p>🚀 <strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul><li><p>Engage customers and understand their needs</p></li><li><p>Build strong relationships and deliver solutions</p></li><li><p>Work closely with mentors on growth strategies</p></li><li><p>Take on leadership responsibilities over time</p></li></ul><p>💼 <strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><ul><li><p>1-to-1 mentorship from industry leaders</p></li><li><p>Clear advancement pathway</p></li><li><p>Entrepreneurial, fast-paced environment</p></li><li><p>Full training provided — no experience needed</p></li></ul><p>👤 <strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li><p>Ambitious, people-oriented individuals</p></li><li><p>Open to learning and personal growth</p></li></ul><p>📩 <strong>Apply now and start building your future with us.</strong></p>",
